  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, toss the chicken with olive oil, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper until coated.",
    "In a large clay pot, cook the chicken over medium-high heat until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the chopped onion, bell pepper, and tomato to the clay pot and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Stir in the crushed sesame seed burger buns and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Transfer the clay pot to the preheated oven and bake for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove the clay pot from the oven and let it cool for 5 minutes.",
    "Serve the paella on a hot stone plate and garnish with chopped fresh parsley."
